[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0868","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0868.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1017","title":"Seattle Labs Emurl 邮件附件脚本执行漏洞","description":"Seattle Labs Emurl 2.0 及更早版本存在不安全存储漏洞，程序将电子邮件附件存入启用了脚本执行的目录中，攻击者可通过发送包含恶意 ASP 文件附件的邮件触发该漏洞，当收件人打开邮件时 ASP 脚本自动执行，导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Seattle Labs Emurl 系列邮件客户端，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1017"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.843","remediation":"在邮件附件存储目录中禁用脚本执行权限，将附件保存目录移出 Web 根目录或在该目录的 IIS 配置中移除 ASP/脚本映射。升级到 Emurl 2.0 以上版本，并配置附件目录无执行权限。如无法升级，可在 IIS 中将附件目录设置为禁止脚本执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93316253431588&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/544","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1017","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1017.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h7mf-q457-42rj/GHSA-h7mf-q457-42rj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/544/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1017.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0868.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1684","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1684.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1018","title":"Linux Kernel IPChains IP 分片绕过安全漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.2.10 及更早版本中的 IPChains 防火墙组件在处理 IP 分片数据包时存在分片重组缺陷，在检查包头前未正确重组 IP 分片，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送多个偏移量为 0 的精心构造的 IP 分片，绕过防火墙过滤规则实现对内部网络的未授权访问。该漏洞影响 Linux 2.2.10 及之前版本内核，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1018"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.960","remediation":"升级至 Linux 内核 2.2.11 及以上版本（该版本已修复 IP 分片重组检查问题），或迁移至 2.4.x/2.6.x 等后续长期支持内核系列。若无法升级内核，可在防火墙规则中添加 `-f` 参数丢弃分片包作为临时缓解：`iptables -A INPUT -f -j DROP`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93312523904591&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/543","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19301","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1018","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1018.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3xc5-vgfg-rqw3/GHSA-3xc5-vgfg-rqw3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/543/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1018.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1684.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0406","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0406.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0710","title":"Squid cachemgr.cgi 未授权连接漏洞","description":"Squid 代理服务器软件在 Red Hat Linux 5.2/6.0 及其他发行版中默认将 cachemgr.cgi 脚本安装于公开 Web 目录下，且未进行充分的访问权限控制。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HTTP 请求直接访问该脚本，将其作为中间代理连接至内部系统，进而实施端口扫描、内网探测等未授权操作。该漏洞影响 Squid 2.2 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至最新版本或限制 cachemgr.cgi 的访问来源。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0710"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.680","remediation":"立即应用 Red Hat RHSA-1999-025 安全公告提供的补丁，升级 Squid 软件包至修复版本。如无法升级，手动删除或移走 Web 目录下的 cachemgr.cgi 文件（通常位于 /usr/share/squid/cgi-bin/cachemgr.cgi），或通过 Apache/Nginx 配置限制对该 CGI 脚本的访问，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 地址访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://fedoranews.org/updates/FEDORA--.shtml","http://www.debian.org/security/2004/dsa-576","http://www.redhat.com/archives/fedora-announce-list/2005-May/msg00025.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-1999-025.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA-2005-489.html","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/archives/rh52-errata-general.html#squid","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2059","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2385","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20465","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0710.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/6df16fc0c02ccadd2d0fbb0029e3db345d75f1c8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0710.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0710","https://github.com/microsoft/azurelinux/blob/9f7efd452e708e85d3f0f58a263f5d82f56f72af/specs/s/squid/squid.spec","https://github.com/squid-cache/squid/blob/6f4c814b8181c38c56be817f2d339936b63b408f/ChangeLog","https://github.com/grafeas/grafeas/blob/448cd756a92f62111ecf96509c66267421396826/go/v1beta1/storage/testobjects.go","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0710.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0710.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/fedora_2005-373.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qhrx-x4p7-jr4j/GHSA-qhrx-x4p7-jr4j.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0406.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0406.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0406.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0014","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0224","title":"Microsoft Windows NT Messenger Service 长用户名拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Messenger 服务在解析超长用户名时存在边界处理缺陷，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的超长用户名数据包，触发服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击者无需复杂工具即可通过标准网络协议发包实施攻击，影响 Windows NT 4.0 全版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0224"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-07-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.923","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 4.0 的 Service Pack 5 (SP5) 或更高版本，该补丁修复了 Messenger Service 对畸形用户名处理不当的问题。对于已停止支持的旧系统，建议升级至 Windows Server 2003 或更高版本；若无法升级，可在服务管理器中禁用 \"Messenger\" 服务以消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0224","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/329","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0224.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0224","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0224.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0224.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0575","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0575.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0811","title":"Samba smbd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Samba 2.0.5 之前版本的 smbd 守护进程在处理畸形消息命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可向目标 Samba 服务发送特制的恶意消息包触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃或实现本地权限提升，获取系统高权限。该漏洞影响所有 Samba 2.0.5 之前版本，CVSS 评分为 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0811"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.360","remediation":"升级 Samba 至 2.0.5 或更高版本，该版本修复了 smbd 进程处理畸形消息命令时的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可在 smb.conf 中限制可访问 smbd 的源 IP 地址范围作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/536","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19428"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0575.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0808","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0808.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0810","title":"Samba nmbd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Samba 2.0.5 的 NetBIOS 名称服务守护进程（nmbd）存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标发送特制的 NetBIOS 名称服务请求数据包，导致 nmbd 进程崩溃或进入死循环，从而停止响应正常的名称解析请求，造成网络服务中断。该漏洞影响 Samba 2.0.5 及之前版本，攻击复杂度低，无需用户交互。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0810"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.230","remediation":"升级 Samba 至 2.0.5 或更高版本（推荐 2.0.6），该版本修复了 nmbd 处理异常 NetBIOS 名称时陷入死循环或崩溃的问题。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面过滤 UDP 137 端口的入站 NetBIOS 名称服务请求作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0810"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0808.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0994","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0994.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1165","title":"GNU fingerd 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"GNU fingerd 1.37 存在权限处理不当漏洞，程序在访问用户信息前未能正确放弃特权，导致本地攻击者可通过两种方式利用：一是在 .fingerrc 文件中放置恶意程序获取 root 权限；二是利用 .plan、.forward 或 .project 文件的符号链接读取系统任意文件。该漏洞影响 GNU fingerd 1.37 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，需手动修复或禁用 finger 服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1165"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:51.533","remediation":"建议立即升级 GNU fingerd 至 1.37 以上版本，该版本已修复权限提升漏洞。更推荐的方案是直接禁用 finger 服务（systemctl disable fingerd 或在 inetd/xinetd 配置中注释 finger 行），因为该服务在现代网络环境中已无必要且存在安全隐患。如必须使用，应限制 .plan/.forward/.project 等文件的写权限，禁止普通用户在这些文件中使用符号链接，并删除 .fingerrc 文件的可执行权限以防止恶意程序执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93268249021561&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/2478","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/535"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0994.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-01338","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-01338.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1338","title":"DeleGate 代理服务器 DGROOT 目录权限许可漏洞","description":"DeleGate 代理 5.9.3 及更早版本在 DGROOT 目录中创建的文件和目录具有全局可写权限，导致本地用户可修改或删除敏感文件","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1338"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-21","updated":"2024-06-16","remediation":"升级到 Delegate proxy 5.9.4 或更高版本，或手动修复 DGROOT 目录权限","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93259112204664&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-01338.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0408","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0408.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0721","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0/2000 LSA 子系统拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 本地安全认证子系统（LSA）存在输入验证不当漏洞（CWE-20），远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 LSA 请求报文触发该漏洞，导致 LSA 服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可发起攻击，利用难度较低。微软已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0721"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.073","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-020 提供的安全更新补丁（KB Q231457），该补丁修复了 LSA 子系统对畸形请求的输入验证缺陷。如无法安装补丁，可在防火墙层面限制对 LSA 相关端口的非授权访问作为临时缓解措施。鉴于 Windows NT 4.0 和 Windows 2000 已停止支持，建议升级到受支持的 Windows 版本以获得持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231457","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-049.shtml","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-020","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0721.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0721","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0721.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0721.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hr94-mwmh-6848/GHSA-hr94-mwmh-6848.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0721.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0408.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0306","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0306.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0692","title":"Cray Unicos Array Services 守护进程默认认证绕过漏洞","description":"Cray UNICOS 操作系统中的 Array Services 守护进程（arrayd）存在默认配置不当漏洞。该服务在默认安装情况下关闭了身份认证机制，导致远程攻击者无需任何凭证即可直接连接 arrayd 端口，并以 root 权限在目标系统上执行任意命令。攻击条件极低——只需目标开放 arrayd 服务且使用默认配置即可完成利用。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，影响 Cray UNICOS 系列操作系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0692"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.550","remediation":"升级 Cray Unicos 至厂商修复版本（如 8.0 及以上补丁级别），或修改 arrayd 配置文件启用认证（设置 require_authentication=yes）。如无法升级，使用 iptables 限制仅有信任管理节点可访问 arrayd 端口（默认 TCP/1050）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-052.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0692","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/479b29734109e75b43136719820cebdc00fad096/1999/CVE-1999-0692/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0692.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-g2hc-xmvw-hhph/GHSA-g2hc-xmvw-hhph.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0692.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9e4ef6a4-48d0-4517-8dd9-a548963a1dd4.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0306.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1092","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1092.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1378","title":"dbmlparser CGI 留言本程序任意文件读取漏洞","description":"dbmlparser.exe 是一款 CGI 留言簿程序，其 chroot 操作实现存在缺陷，导致 chroot 限制未能正确生效。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可利用路径遍历技术绕过目录隔离，读取服务器上的任意文件，包括配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息。该漏洞影响使用该 CGI 程序的 Web 服务器，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。由于该程序年代久远且已停止维护，建议迁移至其他受支持的留言簿解决方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1378"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:18.727","remediation":"立即停止使用 dbmlparser.exe 程序，该软件已停止维护且无安全更新。如必须运行，在 Web 服务器层面限制 CGI 脚本执行权限，仅允许访问特定数据目录；同时配置 Web 服务器（如 Apache 的 mod_rewrite 或 IIS 的 URL 重写）过滤 DBMLFILE 参数中的路径遍历字符（如 ../），并确保 CGI 进程以最低权限账户运行，限制其可读取的文件系统范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93250710625956&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1092.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1683","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1683.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1011","title":"Microsoft Data Access Components (MDAC) RDS 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Data Access Components (MDAC) 中的远程数据服务 (RDS) DataFactory 组件暴露了不安全的内部方法，远程攻击者可通过 IIS 发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用该组件绕过安全限制直接执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0/4.0、MDAC 2.1 等组件，攻击无需身份认证，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。微软已发布安全公告及补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1011"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.110","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-025 提供的补丁，或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本（默认禁用 RDS DataFactory）。如无法升级，删除注册表键 `HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\W3SVC\\Parameters\\ADCLaunch\\RDSServer.DataFactory` 以禁用该危险组件，同时在 IIS 管理器中移除 `/msadc/` 虚拟目录映射。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-054.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/272","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-004","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-025","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/529","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19424","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1011","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/e4734a5d374932e0e8adfb714d6049181237b752/1999/CVE-1999-1011/README.md","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1011.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1011.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qcm7-2qvw-4c58/GHSA-qcm7-2qvw-4c58.json","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1683.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1683.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1683.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1700","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1700.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1086","title":"Novell NetWare IPX 管理会话伪骗权限提升漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 5及更早版本在IPX协议上运行且数据包签名级别低于3时存在安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过伪造IPC分片数据包中的MAC地址来欺骗NetWare核心协议(NCP)调用，从而在未经授权的情况下获取管理员权限。该漏洞危害严重，CVSS评分10.0，可导致目标系统完全受控。建议升级数据包签名级别至3或以上以进行防护。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1086"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:41.520","remediation":"将 NetWare 服务器 NCF 文件中 `SET PACKET SIGNATURE LEVEL` 设置为 3 或更高，强制要求 IPX 数据包签名验证，防止 MAC 地址欺骗攻击。如无法调整签名级别，可考虑禁用 IPX 协议并迁移至 TCP/IP 网络，或使用 VLAN 隔离限制攻击来源。建议升级至 Novell 6 及以上版本以获得完整修复。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93214475111651&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/528","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1086","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1086.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qhf9-4cg8-h46m/GHSA-qhf9-4cg8-h46m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1086.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000696.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1700.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1116","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1116.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1460","title":"BMC Patrol SNMP Agent 本地文件创建权限提升漏洞","description":"BMC Software Patrol SNMP Agent 3.2.07 之前版本存在权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 snmpmagt 程序传递目标文件路径作为第二个参数，以 root 权限创建任意全局可写文件。攻击者利用此漏洞可覆盖系统关键文件或植入恶意脚本，从而获取完全控制权。该漏洞影响 Patrol 3.2.07 之前所有版本，需本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1460"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:29.277","remediation":"升级 BMC PATROL SNMP Agent 至 3.2.07 或更高版本，该版本修复了 snmpmagt 程序未正确校验文件路径参数的问题。如无法升级，限制本地用户对 snmpmagt 程序的执行权限，仅允许受信任的管理员账户使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93198293132463&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93372579004129&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/525","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19422","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e6863af1ae3bb1cd8c56c1f1aac61d836661ac74/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1460.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1460","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1460.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1460.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j5w8-q6hm-5q59/GHSA-j5w8-q6hm-5q59.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb